cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper deals with transfer learning in the biomedical and clinical domain using recurrent neural models for relation classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and machine learning. The paper also discusses the effectiveness of transfer learning frameworks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks also suggests the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks for image classification, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the use of recurrent neural networks suggests the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
